Class CharacterArrayClobType

    java.io.Serializable, BasicType, ProcedureParameterExtractionAware<java.lang.Character[]>, ProcedureParameterNamedBinder, SingleColumnType<java.lang.Character[]>, StringRepresentableType<java.lang.Character[]>, Type
    public class CharacterArrayClobType
extends AbstractSingleColumnStandardBasicType<java.lang.Character[]>
    A type that maps between CLOB and Character[]

    Essentially a MaterializedClobType but represented as a Character[] in Java rather than String.
